    "about": "Founder and Managing Director of FSF Group, a UK-based consultancy focused on AI, data analytics, and emerging technology strategy.\n\nMy work bridges US and UK technology ecosystems, drawing on hands-on experience gained during an extended professional period in the United States. While in the US, I developed a strong foundation in artificial intelligence and data-driven decision-making, working alongside leading practitioners and gaining exposure to cutting-edge AI research and deployment.\n\nIn April 2025, I worked part-time as a Data Analyst (Contract) with Thinking Machines Lab, supporting analytical and data-focused initiatives within an advanced research environment. This role strengthened my applied understanding of AI systems, data pipelines, and real-world model evaluation.\n\nAfter returning to the UK in August 2025, I founded FSF Group to provide organisations with practical AI insight, strategic guidance, and access to transatlantic expertise. FSF Group supports clients seeking to understand, adopt, and operationalise AI responsibly and effectively.\n\nMy background also includes early-stage company formation, commercial operations, and strategic oversight, giving me a grounded, business-first approach to emerging technologies.\n",
